flowchart TD
    A[SQL 表 / 索引 / TOAST relation] --> B[pg_class: OID 与 relfilenode]
    B --> C{Fork}
    C --> C1[main: 数据页]
    C --> C2[fsm: 近似空闲空间]
    C --> C3[vm: all-visible / all-frozen]
    C --> C4[init: 仅 unlogged relation]
    C1 --> D[Segment: base, .1, .2 ...]
    D --> E[Block/Page: 通常 8 KiB]
    E --> F[PageHeaderData]
    E --> G[ItemId / Line Pointer 数组]
    E --> H[Heap Tuple 数据区]
    H --> I[Tuple Header]
    H --> J[NULL bitmap + padding + attributes]
    J --> K{大 varlena 值?}
    K -->|可内联| H
    K -->|压缩/外置| L[关联 TOAST table + index]
